data.title: Population And Society in the United States for Persons Naturalized (Metrics), Burkina Faso (Country Of Birth): Data and Trends
data.meta_description: USAFacts -- In 2021 (most recent) there were 510 Persons naturalized in the United States for Burkina Faso (COUNTRY OF BIRTH). This increased by 134 or 35.64% from 2020. Highest: 510 in 2021. Lowest: 166 in 2012.
